			<div class="content">I think its 67 when charm xp begins to be crappy in hoh and is totally dead at 68.  I remember the sentries being randomly 61 or 62, so at 67 you lose the bonus xp on about half of your kills and at 68 you lose it for the other half.  Its easy to tell at any rate as you can just watch your %xp / kill at each level (i think it was around 5.4% at level 65) and watch for the level at which it drops precipitously.</div>

