			<div class="content">Once HoH become's craptacular XP, you can move to Noble's Causeway like the above poster said.  After that gets trivial, you can move to the murk caves in WoS.  But before you do that, I would suggest getting all of the &quot;save my ass stat wise&quot; aa's.  Those murks hit pretty hard.  And if you can, find a (wanna say disease) resist buff to keep the murk venom off of you.</div>

