			<div class="content">I never used blur back in hoh.  Breaking charm before your pet kills the target mob accomplishes the same thing and for far less mana.  I always killed them in pairs, breaking charm on my pet before it could finish off the target leaving 2 mobs each with 1-2 nukes worth of hps.  It always seemed far more efficient than letting the pet steal xp as the limiting factor was availability of nearby mobs rather than mana for me.</div>

