			<h3 ><a href="#p129570"></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" />by <strong>Falla</strong> &raquo; Sun Dec 24, 2006 10:53 am </p>

			

			<div class="content">Just an update on this, I have been hunting the South Hero Shrine on an alt.
<br />
<br />The mobs in the old safe hall next to Valorian Guardian Kriek, can be pulled without aggroing him.
<br />
<br />At level 65, mobs yielded just over 6% per kill
<br />
<br />At level 66, mobs yielded between approx 5.5 - 5.75 per kill
<br />
<br />At level 67, mobs ( apart from the Hero Shrine Guardians ) were all still dark blue and yielded 5% per kill
<br />
<br />Falla</div>

			

