		<div class="postbody">
			

			<h3 ><a href="#p129586"></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" />by <strong>Hardy</strong> &raquo; Wed Dec 27, 2006 8:39 am </p>

			

			<div class="content">I'd look to the DoN armour/augs to upgrade your armour - it's what I did when I returned before getting some nice new tss stuff.  Last time I was in the bazzar the crystals were going for about 25pp (on Povar).  
<br />
<br />I still dabble in HoH when I've a little time to kill - I use pretty much the same method as you, just I got lazier these days!  I don't both with Paci I just root one of the Guardians, tash his mate as he comes to me &amp; run to the other end of the corridor.  By the time I get there (with run5) he's generally out of range so easy to CoD.  Then go back &amp; kill the rooted one &amp; the other 3.  I always haste the pet &amp; slow the target.  Can clear both sides &amp; the middle (except the named in the centre), both hero shrine guardians &amp; the wandering named before they repop.  
<br />
<br />The exp is not great (1.5% aa per kill at 75) but the loots are OK - lots of parchments &amp; hero parts (which go for 200pp) so it helps fund other stuff.
<br />
<br />I'll look out for you next time I pop in there <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":)" title="icon_biggrin.gif" /></div>

